{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"id":"53921bc5-af00-4820-9b18-13725d34b66b","level":1},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jopus个人说明书"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"id":"23c0d6f4-bed3-4152-a70d-dadffd6b1a56","level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"前言"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"750b3ba7-41af-48e0-ab5e-34c614768089"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"这是我的个人说明书，这个说明书是我和这个世界的交流方式，写这个说明书也是一个梳理自己的过程。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"d1a23f37-503a-4ee9-9c87-657c3d92a02c"}},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"f2a7faaf-b31c-48b7-b4f2-33db2af28a37"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"我认为个人应该尽量多的把经验或思考都落实到文字上存档起来。人生短暂，总不应该花太多的时间在迷茫上，写作是个逻辑思考的过程，通过写成文档更能方便他人查阅。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"5c320119-f289-4501-a12b-5d1938a5cb62"}},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"id":"e880131c-db7d-48e1-a058-a2690c280511","level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个说明书为谁而写？"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"2802d1c9-16f7-483a-8440-fed9f9db32b8"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个是为我自己书写，更是为了每一个想了解我的人而写。我喜欢通过文字去了解一个人，我也希望别人也能通过文字了解我。我更希望我通过记录这些，让我也更了解自己。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"0846e976-f80a-4045-ae0e-16cac0c4c181"}},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"id":"376801d6-57ec-46c6-8b08-298e28f3fae2","level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"说明书里记录了什么？"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"e9601a5e-1357-4b2a-a36d-c2964076808a"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"这里会记录我所的读的书、我喜欢看的电影、我的兴趣爱好、我的工作习惯、我所认知的概念，总之，是我能告知并写成文档的一切。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"dc8c0ce2-8dca-4b36-bc94-b8ae59234aa7"}},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"id":"0af42477-8f2b-46d5-b904-ebf1312204e5","level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"个人说明书目录"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"f05b35c2-39c0-4072-8b9a-8bc04e0656e0"}},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"5c754931-1381-4097-8bc6-583ec403ce5c"},"content":[{"type":"card","attrs":{"cardId":"1186d249-ed1a-48c1-971d-786f62b5817a"}}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"a099a78a-9f7c-4810-a832-7d5114da508b"},"content":[{"type":"card","attrs":{"cardId":"8e062dc1-bdf1-4b80-9ad7-6dfe6781b56f"}}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"d1dcc805-ca47-42ca-b77e-9ce45de23485"}},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"d7d665ff-da99-45ec-b753-60f868fb41d3"}}]}
